Rule	What it means	Error you will see
All fields mandatory	Every field (except Comments) must be filled in	Mandatory fields left empty: [field names]
Dropdowns must be selected	Cannot leave a dropdown on “-- Select --”	Please select a value for: [field names]
No multiple spaces	Only one space between words	Multiple consecutive spaces found in: [field names]
No leading/trailing spaces	No spaces at the start or end of a value	Leading or trailing spaces found in: [field names]
Confluence URL prefix	HLD and IFM must start with https://colesgroup.atlassian.net/	URL must begin with https://colesgroup.atlassian.net/ for: [field names]
Database Name prefix	Must start with DB_CORE_	Value must begin with DB_CORE_ for: Database Name
Expiration Date	Required when Encrypted = YES	Mandatory fields left empty: Expiration Date
