Character limit	Text fields: 500 characters max. Comments: 2000 max	Field stops accepting input at the limit
Auto uppercase	Key fields are converted to uppercase automatically	No error — happens automatically
You will also see small inline warnings below individual fields as you type (e.g., if you enter multiple spaces or the wrong URL prefix). These help you fix issues before hitting Save.

